    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "I saw another field full of all kinds of flowers, and as I plucked them, I cried out, &ldquo;They will never fade!&rdquo; Next I saw a field of tall grass, most glorious to behold; it was living green and had a reflection of silver and gold as it waved proudly to the glory of King Jesus. Then we entered a field full of all kinds of beasts&mdash;the lion, the lamb, the leopard, and the wolf, all together in perfect union. We passed through the midst of them, and they followed on peaceably after.",
