    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "There every power will be developed, every capability increased. The grandest enterprises will be carried forward, the loftiest aspirations will be reached, the highest ambitions realized. And still there will arise new heights to surmount, new wonders to admire, new truths to comprehend, fresh objects to call forth the powers of body and mind and soul.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">8<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ed 307.1\" data-link=\"29.1611\">Education, 307</span>.</span></a></sup>",
