    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "To us who are standing on the very verge of their fulfillment, of what deep moment, what living interest, are these delineations of the things to come&mdash;events for <span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"550\"></span> which, since our first parents turned their steps from Eden, God&apos;s children have watched and waited, longed and prayed!",
