    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Fellow pilgrim, we are still amid the shadows and turmoil of earthly activities, but soon our Saviour is to appear to bring deliverance and rest. Let us by faith behold the blessed hereafter, as pictured by the hand of God.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">10<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"PK 731.1\" data-link=\"88.3281\">Prophets and Kings, 731, 732</span>.</span></a></sup>",
